fichier source liste:

deb http://deb.debian.org/debian jessie main non-free
deb-src http://deb.debian.org/debian jessie main non-free

deb http://deb.debian.org/debian jessie-updates main non-free
deb-src http://deb.debian.org/debian jessie-updates main non-free

deb http://security.debian.org/ jessie/updates main non-free
deb-src http://security.debian.org/ jessie/updates main non-free

deb http://packages.dotdeb.org jessie all


